    Service page

    {% extends "service.html" %}

    This template is for service start pages on tonbridgespiritualist.com.
    These should not be hosted on your service and should instead be hosted on alphatsc.

    Home page

    {% extends "home.html" %}

    This template is for use in producing the home page of your service.

    ! Warning If your service is a process e.g application, you should instead use the service template, making the start button link to the first question on your service, and then launch a pull request to insert it into the alphatsc GitHub repository.

    For help visit the publishing page
